data.description: Check out this lovely 2-story residence with a manicured landscape, mature shade tree, a 2-car garage, an RV gate, & a cozy porch! Entering, you will discover tall ceilings, tile flooring in high-traffic areas, soft carpet in all the right places, charming light fixtures, and archways. Receive guests in the well-sized living/dining room. The perfectly-flowing great room boasts bountiful natural light & has sliding glass doors leading to the back. Functional kitchen offers plenty of beautiful wood cabinets, built-in appliances, ample counter space, & a breakfast nook. Upstairs, the sizeable loft is great for a workout area. Large main retreat has plush carpet & a private bath w/a walk-in closet.
